NameFlagsCard.TypeDescription & Constraints
Extension 0..*ExtensionAvailable time
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Open by value:url
extension:daysOfWeek S0..*ExtensionDays of week
url 1..1uri"daysOfWeek"
value[x]:valueCode 1..1codeDays of the week - mon|tue|wed|thu|fri|sat|sun
Binding: DaysOfWeek (required)
extension:allDay S0..1ExtensionAll day
url 1..1uri"allDay"
value[x]:valueBoolean 1..1booleanAll day
extension:availableStartTime S0..1ExtensionAvailable start time
url 1..1uri"availableStartTime"
value[x]:valueTime 1..1timeAvailable start time
extension:availableEndTime S0..1ExtensionAvailable end time
url 1..1uri"availableEndTime"
value[x]:valueTime 1..1timeAvailable end time
url 1..1uri"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/vhdir/StructureDefinition/contactpoint-availabletime"
value[x] S0..0

Documentation for this format
